    "encrypted": "false",
    "long_instructions": "## Interior Design\r\n\r\nUse AI Chat to help plan out ideas for decorating a room.\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n\r\n1. **Upload an image** from the Library.\r\n2. Decide which part of the room you would like to redesign. Here are some ideas:\r\n\t- Furniture & Layout\r\n    - Lighting\r\n    - Color & Walls\r\n    - Texture & Fabrics\r\n    - You can use AI chat to help you brainstorm more ideas if you'd like!\r\n3. **Modify** the following prompt and press **Send**.:\r\n\r\n>Help me brainstorm ideas for **[insert area of interest here]** in this room.\r\n\r\n4. Read AI Chat's response.\r\n5. **Experiment**: Test how AI responds to different inputs:\r\n    - **Modify your prompt** by changing which part of the room to focus on\r\n    - **Upload a new image** to get a different response\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n::: details [<i class=\"fa fa-picture-o\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> **How do I upload a file I found?**]\r\n- Download the file (image or PDF) on to your device\r\n- Click the button labeled **Upload** below your chat input.\r\n- Choose **From Device**\r\n- Then locate the file on your device.\r\n- When you find the file to upload, select it and then click **Open**.\r\n- You should see the image get added to the message being sent to AI Chat.\r\n:::",
